OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry start with some
OL,6,Fbrightness. Then outbreaks of rain
OL,7,Fspread east, becoming heavy for a time
OL,8,Fin the afternoon. Breezy for a time in
OL,9,Fafternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FLargely cloudy through the
OL,12,Fevening and overnight with outbreaks
OL,13,Fof rain, occasionally heavy at first.
OL,14,FSome drier and clearer spells may
OL,15,Fdevelop at times overnight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FAny cloud and rain at first
OL,18,Fwill gradually clear to bright or
OL,19,Fsunny spells in the morning. Bright
OL,20,Fspells and a few showers developing in
OL,21,Fthe afternoon, heavy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
