OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FBright
OL,6,For sunny spells and scattered showers
OL,7,FTuesday and Wednesday, some heavy and
OL,8,Fthundery. Dry, bright start on
OL,9,FThursday, cloud and rain spreading
OL,10,Feast later.
